			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Friendship letter from Maria Teles to Madam Joana Perpétua Henriques Cabreira.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author tells the addressee about the value of a stolen ring.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">Joana Perpétua Henriques Cabreira accused Pantaleão José Gonçalves, a shop owner, of taking ownership of a diamond ring which had been handed in to him as a guarantee for buying a hat.
							This letter, written by a complaining friend, was used as evidence of the ring’s value.
						</p>
				<p sameAs="text">«Dearest madam.</p></change>
